Suite/Test/Step Name: 02 Pesanan Tempatan Cara Bayaran CEK Dengan Pemfaktoran
Test Cases/Perolehan/005 Terimaan Barang Perkhidmatan/002 Proses Kemasukan Terimaan Barang - CEK
Description: Penyedia will create REKOD BARU using dokumen ID from Pesanan Tempatan
Open browser and navigate to Homepage URL
Click on Menu Sisi to display Menu selections
Click on Menu sisi Kemasukan Terimaan Barang atau perkhidmatan
Click No Dokumen drop down list
Set text RekodID based on the variable get from Pelulus page on Pesanan Tempatan
Select the No Dokumen displayed after the filter
Click on OK to close the prompt box
Click on drop down Jenis terimaan

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Perolehan/006 Arahan Bayaran/002 Arahan Bayaran - CEK
Description: Create new REKOD BARU for arahan bayaran after kemasukan terimaan barang is saved
Click on Menu Sisi to display Menu selections
Click on Menu sisi and select Arahan Bayaran
Click Jenis Baucar Bayaran drop down
Select Kod Jenis Baucar Bayaran that is ARAHAN BAYARAN-PESANAN TEMPATAN
Get todays year, date and time
